            <div class="title">
                National Memorial To His Late Majesty King George The Fifth
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1939-06-20/debates/af65080d-5aa5-4f93-ad0d-1cac7eaaa57f/MinistryOfSupplyBill" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
